author: Reuters
title: DIARY - Today in Washington - July 22
text:
ALL TIMES IN EDT/GMT
0700/1100: The USDA issues weekly world rice price.
0900/1300: The Federal Housing Finance Agency issues House Price Index for May.
1000/1400: The National Association of Realtors issues Existing Home Sales for June.
1030/1430: The Energy Information Administration issues weekly petroleum stocks and output data.
The Association of American Railroads issues Weekly Traffic of Major Railroads.
1500/1900: The USDA issues monthly Cold Storage.
